      <h4 class="policy_h">Payment Processing</h4>
      <h6>Overview</h6>

      <ul>
        <li class=" d-flex  ">
          <i class="fas fa-circle"></i>
          <p class="policy_p">eboxtickets payment processing. Credit/debit card bookings processed online via eboxtickets merchant services gateway. Income is held in a trust account and will be transferred to the Event Organiser at the conclusion of their event</p>
