      <p class="policy_p">The varying exchange and refund policies set forth by our Event Organisers prohibit eboxtickets from issuing exchanges or refunds after a booking is placed. If a refund or exchange is requested by a Customer, the Customer is advised to contact the Event Organiser directly to process their request as per the Event or Venue's own exchange and refund policy.</p>
